results.name: Falcon
results.description: With a mental connection to all birds and a suit that gives him wings to fly, The Falcon has been both the partner to Captain America and an Avenger himself. Whether as a super hero or in his secret identity of social worker Sam Wilson, The Falcon dedicates his life to standing up for others.

items.name: Captain America & the Falcon: Secret Empire (2005)

results.name: Falcon/Sam Wilson (MAA)
results.description: Recruited from S.H.I.E.L.D. by his hero and mentor Tony Stark, Falcon is the Avengers' newest and youngest recruit. Like Tony, Sam is a genius with machines and technology. What he lacks in experience, Sam makes up in enthusiasm and determination. Falcon's suit of armor comes fully stocked with holographic wings, explosive flechettes, and retractable talons.

results.name: Fantastic Four
results.description: After being exposed to cosmic rays, Reed Richards, Susan Storm, Ben Grimm and Johnny Storm found they had amazing new powers. Reed Richards found he has the ability to stretch his body in any way he wanted, while Susan Storm can turn herself, objects and other people invisible. Ben Grimm transformed into a rocky, super-strong behemoth and Johnny Storm has the ability to set himself on fire. Dubbed the Fantastic Four, Mr. Fantastic, Invisible Woman, Thing and the Human Torch are Marvel's First Family.
